{"tid":1533550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家認清事實，唔好高估自己嘅運動能力！","createTime":"2019-09-02T17:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T00:19:17.000Z","uid":68033,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0066d42c1a048a06724f124c507873d07b37a7d4","tid":1533550,"uid":68033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:53:16.000Z","msg":"想就返近幾日嘅拘留行動講：<br />\n<br />\n黑警濫捕濫權係事實，<br />\n唔需要再作討論；<br />\n但因為大家都已知黑警係會對被捕義士虐打、侮辱、性侵犯，<br />\n所以希望大家可以係<span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span>嘅情況下先去屌差佬。<br />\n<br />\n當中最緊要係希望大家特別係街坊同學生，<br />\n一定<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以</span></span>高估自己嘅運動能力！！！<br />\n雖然大家成日笑鳩黑警大肚腩、戇鳩，<br />\n但唔可以否認係有大量手足係因為走唔切而被捕。<br />\n就算兩者防線相差一百米大家都唔好以為好安全：<br />\n1. 佢受過訓練，而且直線衝黎途中係冇障礙；<br />\n2. 就算你保特咁快，你都唔可以確定你轉身係冇人阻住你跑。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一百米其實黑警慢極呀都係20秒內嘅事。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望唔會再有手足因為咁被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n願榮光歸香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"592916551895149ff77812da9fc6eda86167c3c7","tid":1533550,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:56:14.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷史法師！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></span></span>遇怪魔想變大個，就一定一定要睇！<br />\n<br />